<pre>
F	Foxtrot		Fox-trot		
G	Golf		Golf		
H	Hotel		Ho-tel		
I	India		In-dia		
J	Juliett		Giu-li-et		
</pre>
113&
<pre>
K	Kilo		Ki-lo		
L	Lima		Li-ma		
M	Mike		Maik	

Litera	Cuvântul de cod	Pronuntia	
